      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>A declaration recording an agreement between
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">Mulla Jawad</persName>,
               <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">Mulla Ahsanullah</persName>
                and
               <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">Mulla Abbas</persName>
                about using land they owned in the neighbourhood (muhalla) of Hassanabad for a
               graveyard, a mosque and a public bath (hammam). The agreement relates to properties
               that were part of a charitable endowment (waqf).</p>
         </abstract>
