         <div xml:lang="per" xml:id="orig_div1" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>باعث تحریر این چند سطور آنکه چون زمین مقبره جد مرحومی
               <persName ref="#mullaAbdulGhani">ملا عبد الغنی</persName>
                مغفور در محله
               <placeName ref="#hassanabad">حسن آباد</placeName>
               <lb/>باختتام رسیده بود موجب آن
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">ملا جواد</persName>
                مرحوم یک قطعه زمین در آن محله
               <lb/>بابت مقبره خرید نمود و
               <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">ملا احسن الله</persName>
                و
               <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">ملا عباس </persName>
               را هم در همان محله زمینی
               <lb/>موجود بود در آن ایّام
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">ملا جواد</persName>
                را هوس تعمیر مسجد و حمام وقفی در
               <placeName ref="#hassanabad">حسن آباد</placeName>
               <lb/>مگر زمینی که لایق تعمیر آن می بود مسیر نشده با
               <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">ملا احسن الله</persName>
                و
               <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">ملا عباس</persName>
               <lb/>مصلحت نمودند که بر زمین موجوده شما مسجد و حمام تیار می سازیم و زمین
               <lb/>نو خرید ما برای مقبره مثل سابقه مشترک در میان ما و شما ماند چنانچه در همان
               <lb/>ایام زمین
               <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">ملا احسن الله</persName>
                و
               <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">ملا عباس</persName>
                تحت تعمیر مسجد و حمام آمده است
               <lb/>و زمین
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">ملا جواد</persName>
                زیر مقبره مانده الحال نظر بر گردش اوضاع زمانه نموده
               <lb/>این کاغذ در میان برادری خود باقرار جانبین تحریر کرده شد که
               <lb/>عند الحاجت بکار آید
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
                المرقوم
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">دهم شهر رجب المرجب سنه
                  <num>۱۲۶۶</num>
               </date>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p><lb/>The reason for writing these few lines is that, the graveyard of the respected
               ancestor
               <persName ref="#mullaAbdulGhani">Mulla Abdul Ghani</persName>, who has been forgiven [by God], 
               <lb/>was exhausted [i.e. became full] in the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muhalla">muhalla</ref> of
               <placeName ref="#hassanabad">Hassanabad</placeName>. On that account,
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">Mulla Jawad</persName>, [now] deceased, bought a piece of land in that <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muhalla">muhalla</ref> 
               <lb/>for the purpose of a graveyard while
               <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">Mulla Ahsanullah</persName>
                and
               <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">Mulla Abbas</persName> both
               already possessed land in that very <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muhalla">muhalla</ref>. 
               <lb/>In those days,
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">Mulla Jawad</persName> desired to construct a mosque and charitable [waqfi] hammam in
               <placeName ref="#hassanabad">Hassanabad</placeName>, 
               <lb/>but the land which was suitable for constructing these was not available. He
               consulted with <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">Mulla Ahsanullah</persName>
                and <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">Mulla Abbas</persName> 
               <lb/>[saying] that I will build a dedicated mosque and a hammam on your existing
               land, and the land 
               <lb/>that I have newly purchased will remain for a graveyard, just like the old
               legacy, between you and I. Thus, in those very 
               <lb/>days on the land of
               <persName ref="#mullaAhsanullah">Mulla Ahsanullah</persName>
                and
               <persName ref="#mullaAbbas">Mulla Abbas</persName>, the foundation of the mosque and hammam [was constructed].
               <lb/>And the land of
               <persName ref="#mullaJawad">Mulla Jawad</persName>
                remained under [dedicated to] graves. Currently, with a view to the changing habits of the age, 
               <lb/>this document was written within the community with the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_iqrar">iqrars</ref> of the two
               parties, so that 
               <lb/>in time of need, it may be useful.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
                Written on the
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">10th of the month of Rajab al-Murajjab, year
                  1266</date>.
               </p>
         </div>
